text:
struggling to read a small/specific file from the large zip file? try this
`pip install smart_open`

```import smart_open as so
import zipfile

with so.open('<s3://bucket_name/zipfile.zip>', 'rb') as file_data
  with zipfile.zipfile(file_data) as z:
    with z.open('target_file.csv') as zip_file_data: # or any other file instead of csv
      list_of_lines = zip_file_data.readlines()
      # or any other operation here```
